{"tid":998496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有議員建議睇Av要收稅","createTime":"2019-01-28T04:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T09:34:05.000Z","uid":167330,"like":38,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8b86802590fcda9018fbf8d1bdc0a56b9c9597e2","tid":998496,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"建議收 AV 稅助特朗普興建圍牆 美國議員被指冇腦<br />\n<br />\n有留意國際新聞的話，可能都知道美國總統特朗普為了堅持興建墨西哥邊界圍牆，導致聯邦政府機關需要關閉，至今已經接近一個月。美國國會不願批出 57 億美元興建圍牆的經費，然而一名南方邊境亞利桑那州的議員則想到辦法，透過稅收支付興建圍牆的費用。<br />\n<br />\n這位名叫 Gail Griffin 的州議員日前向眾議院提交法案，要求在亞利桑那州開徵色情內容稅，所有在當地銷售的可上網裝置通通都要安裝「色情內容守門員」軟件。假如網民想瀏覽成人網站就必須支付每次 20 美元的通行費用，假如網民不支付費用下繼續瀏覽色情網站，或者跳過守門員軟件，將會被起訴並有機會判處監禁一年。<br />\n<br />\nGriffin 的提案曝光後，馬上被網友一面倒負評，有網民嘲諷支持特朗普的 Griffin 冇腦。限制網民瀏覽網站本身已經非常荒謬，有墨西哥裔的成人電影演員更無法接受自己認真工作，最後竟然協助特朗普興建墨西哥邊境圍牆。有網民打趣說與其強制安裝「色情內容守門員」軟件，不如搞一個「色情內容導航員」軟件，透過收費協助網民搜尋喜歡的色情內容，這樣為圍牆籌募經費可能會更快更受歡迎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wccjaSJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwccjaSJ.png&h=34a8af4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/01/25/av-tax-to-fun-trumps-mexican-wall/fun-tech/?utm_source=spotim&amp;utm_medium=spotim_recirculation&amp;spotim_referrer=recirculation&amp;spot_im_comment_id=sp_jdnCkfMO_765554_c_A8ibK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F25%2Fav-tax-to-fun-trumps-mexican-wall%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Futm_source%3Dspotim%26utm_medium%3Dspotim_recirculation%26spotim_referrer%3Drecirculation%26spot_im_comment_id%3Dsp_jdnCkfMO_765554_c_A8ibK0&d=WJDHSNsNXgcyXkOr%2BhNZvAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=43b3d831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/01/25/av-tax-to-fun-trumps-mexican-wall/fun-tech/?utm_source=spotim&amp;utm_medium=spotim_recirculation&amp;spotim_referrer=recirculation&amp;spot_im_comment_id=sp_jdnCkfMO_765554_c_A8ibK0</a><br />\n<br />\n每次20美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲貴過買正版av睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b47a249ec8f3cdb2e0cc201a4cf9c51da6f9255","tid":998496,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"鼓勵加多少少去叫雞"},{"pid":"b3473881d553b1786f555ad3e3a47a255ef44940","tid":998496,"uid":52145,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"有墨西哥裔的成人電影演員更無法接受自己認真工作，最後竟然協助特朗普興建墨西哥邊境圍牆。<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08812e994c3c6bb2cb915f859df6199e0fc1c3f7","tid":998496,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b47a249ec8f3cdb2e0cc201a4cf9c51da6f9255","tid":998496,"uid":122134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"鼓勵加多少少去叫雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:39:51.000Z","msg":"原來係想鼓勵色情行業，美國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bbf5ac0f612e031173bce0a31e1ff7aee7b50d","tid":998496,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"懷疑條友應該係單身幾十年嘅老閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0481d195466dd0947be2c345bbbd58e02e0416e","tid":998496,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"又係d死臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6a2117ab1a267dcbbfa48149632760d6194e6d","tid":998496,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68918800ea9b9e340b996d3497546ccd7cd5b7e","tid":998496,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"共和黨豬隊友"},{"pid":"f71e716a06a729975a7a9be37c616c0e7